{
  "title": "9^x − 4·3^x + a = 0 — ровно 2 решения",
  "canvas": {
    "width": 560,
    "height": 440,
    "x_min": -1,
    "x_max": 5,
    "y_min": -1,
    "y_max": 5,
    "x_label": "t",
    "y_label": "y или a"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "text": "Замена $t = 3^x$, $t > 0$. Уравнение принимает вид $t^2 - 4t + a = 0$.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "function_curve",
          "id": "f1",
          "expression": "-(t - 2)**2 + 4",
          "label": "$y = -(t - 2)^2 + 4$",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#2980b9",
            "stroke_width": 2.5
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Критические значения параметра $a$: $a = 0$ и $a = 4$.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "hline",
          "id": "h1",
          "y": 0,
          "label": "$a = 0$",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#e74c3c",
            "dash": "dashed"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "hline",
          "id": "h2",
          "y": 4,
          "label": "$a = 4$",
          "style": {
            "stroke": "#8e44ad",
            "dash": "dashed"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Анализ числа решений в зависимости от $a$.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl1",
          "x": 3,
          "y": 2,
          "text": "2 решения",
          "style": {
            "color": "#27ae60",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl2",
          "x": 1,
          "y": 0.5,
          "text": "1 решение",
          "style": {
            "color": "#888",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "region_label",
          "id": "rl3",
          "x": 4,
          "y": 4.5,
          "text": "1 решение",
          "style": {
            "color": "#888",
            "font_size": 13,
            "background": "rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Закрашиваем область, где уравнение имеет ровно 2 решения.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "filled_between",
          "id": "fb1",
          "upper": "-(t - 2)**2 + 4",
          "lower": "0",
          "x_min": 0,
          "x_max": 4,
          "style": {
            "fill": "rgba(41,128,185,0.18)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "Ответ: $0 < a < 4$.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "filled_region",
          "id": "fr1",
          "points": [
            [
              0,
              0
            ],
            [
              0,
              4
            ],
            [
              4,
              4
            ]
          ],
          "style": {
            "fill": "rgba(155,89,182,0.15)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}